xdi2.core.features.linkcontracts

Class LinkContractBase<N extends XdiEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xdi2.core.features.linkcontracts.LinkContractBase<N>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<LinkContractBase<N>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkContract, LinkContractTemplate

    public abstract class LinkContractBase<N extends XdiEntity>
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<LinkContractBase<N>>
    The base class for XDI link contracts and XDI link contract templates, represented as an XDI entity or variable.
